title: [1508521049] Best British Restaurant: The West House, Secret Diner - Gordon Ramsay
description:
Gordon Ramsay in search of Britain's best restaurant. Top restaurants from around the UK compete to win the title. 

Gordon Ramsay shares the results of a secret diner sent in to british restaurant nominee, The West House.
